# Ignore the entire IDE settings directory rather than cherry-picking
# individual files. Android Studio writes per-developer state into
# .idea/ regularly, and the previous selective-ignore pattern was
# incomplete (e.g. AndroidProjectSystem.xml, compiler.xml, gradle.xml,
# markdown.xml, misc.xml, runConfigurations.xml, vcs.xml all ended up
# tracked). See https://github.com/tejasM17/gemini-bot/issues/7.
.idea/
.DS_Store
/build
/captures
.externalNativeBuild
.cxx
local.properties
